quran[69]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  29,2,"E yim…ìe …ìen sikku …ìe accirte nii, fii …ìe wi'ii: \"Men gom…óinii!\" Hara …ìe fitninaaka"
  29,3,"Gom…óii, Men fitninii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe. Maa Alla fe√±√±in, fii goongu…ìe …ìen, maa O fe√±√±in kadi, fii fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,4,"Kaa huuwu…ìe bon…ói …ìen sikku, wonnde …ìe laawoto Men? ko …ìe √±aawata kon bonii"
  29,5,"Kala taw…óo himo jortii hawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo On"
  29,6,"Kala kadi tii…ónii…óo, ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko yonndinii…óo e tageefo ngon"
  29,7,"∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men momtan …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, Men yo…ìitra …ìe, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  29,8,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on, mo∆¥∆¥ugol e maw…ìe makko …ìen. Si …ìe doolii maa fii sirkangol Lam, ko a alanaa …óum ganndal, wata a …óofto …ìe ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko gollayno…óon"
  29,9,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alla, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men wa…ótidu…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,10,"Hino e jim…ìe …ìen, wi'oowo: \"Men gom…óinii Alla\"; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o wa…óay lorra yim…ìe …ìen, wano lepte Alla …óen. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ìe wi'ay: \"Me…óen wondunoo e mo'on!\" Kere wanaa Alla …ìuri anndude ko woni e …ìer…óe tageefo ngon"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ma O fe√±√±ina kadi fii naafiqii…ìe …ìen"
  29,12,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ani gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon …óin\". Kono …ìe wonaali fawtotoo…ìe hay huunde e goopi ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko …ìe fenoo…ìe"
  29,13,"Kono maa …ìe fawtoo fii teddeendi junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, e teddeendi goo, wonndude e teddeendi ma…ì…ìe ndin. Ko maa …ìe lamndoyee, √ëalnde Darngal, gaay e kon ko …ìe fefindotonoo"
  29,14,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o √±ii…ìi hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, duu…ìi ujunere, ≈ãakku…óum duu…ìi cappan…óe jowi. Waame on nanngi …ìe, hari ko …ìe too√±u…ìe"
  29,15,"Men da…óndi mo, kanko e yim…ìe laana kan; Men wa…ói ka kaawisa tageefo ngon"
  29,16,"(Janto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Rewee Alla, hulon Mo; ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, si woni hi…óon anndi"
  29,17,"Anndee ko reweton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, hi…óon ta∆¥a fenaande. Pellet, …óin …ói rewoton gaanin Alla, …ói waawaa on arsikude; …óa…ì…ìiree arsike on ka Alla, rewon Mo, yetton Mo. Ko ka Makko woni ruttete…óon"
  29,18,"Si on fennii, haray mofte adinoo…ìe kadi fenniino (Nulaa…ìe mun). Alaa ko fawii e Nulaa…óo on, si wanaa yottingol …ìannginngol"
  29,19,"E …ìee yi'aali no Alla fu…ó…óorta tagu ngun, refti O ruttay ngu? Pellet, …óum wonii ko newanii Alla"
  29,20,"Maaku: \"Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O fu…ó…óori tagu ngun. Refti Alla taga tagu sakkitoru ngun. Pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  29,21,"Himo lepte mo O muuyani, O yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  29,22,"On wonaali laawotoo…ìe ka leydi, wanaa ka kammu; alanaa on gaanin Alla, woni gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  29,23,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Alla …óen, e hawroygol e Makko ngol, …ìen ta∆¥ike e yurmeende Am, …ìen …óon, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe"
  29,24,"Jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Waree mo, maa sunnon mo\". Kono Alla da…óndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óim…ìe"
  29,25,"O maaki: \"Anndee ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yi…óindiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, √ëalnde Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi hu…óo yoga, hara non, jaa∆¥orde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara walloo…ìe alanaa on"
  29,26,"Luutu gom…óini mo. O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,27,"Men ye…ói mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Men wa…ói e geyngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Men okki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  29,28,"(Janto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen : \" E on aray e pankare, …óe gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun"
  29,29,"E on aray yottagol e wor…ìe …ìen? palo…óon kadi e laawol? Huuwon ko mbatirdu mon ko a√±inii?\" Kono jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen wonaano, si wanaa wiide …ìe: \"Addan men lepte Alla …óen, si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen"
  29,30,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, wallam e hoore yim…ìe bonnoo…ìe …ìen"
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ìe wi\"i: \"Menen, ko men halkoo…ìee yim…ìe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ìe mayre laatike too√±oo…ìe"
  29,32,"O maaki: \"Kono Luutu no ton!\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko menen …ìuri anndude fii won…ìe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen, si wanaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ìe …ìen"
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ìe Amen …ìen hewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ì…ìe, …ìernde makko …ìi…ótorii fii ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu, wata a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ìe ma an e …ìeynguure maa nden, si wanaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ìe …ìen"
  29,34,"Ko men jippinoo…ìe lepte e yim…ìe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ìe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon"
  29,35,"Gom…óii Men accii e nden (saare), maande …ìanngunde, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe …ìen"
  29,36,"(Men nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla, jortoron √ëalannde sakkitiinde nden, wata woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ìe"
  29,37,"Kono …ìe fenni mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ìe, …ìe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìe jiccii…ìe-maayi"
  29,38,"(Men halki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. Gom…óii caambbeje ma…ì…ìe …óin …ìannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ìe, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, ndu sakkii …ìe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ìe rentunoo…ìe"
  29,39,"(Men halki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. Gom…óii le, Muusaa addanii …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji, kono …ìe townitii ka leydi, …ìe wonaano laawotoo…ìe"
  29,40,"Kala ma…ì…ìe, Men leptirno junuubi mun …óin: no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men wuurti henndu e mun; no e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe haacaango halki; no e ma…ì…ìe, mo Men mutini …óum ka leydi, no e ma…ì…ìe kadi, …ìe Men yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali too√±oowo …ìe; si ko woni, ko kam…ìe too√±unoo ko'e ma…ì…ìe"
  29,41,"Misal …ìen jogitii…ìe gaanin Alla rewetee…ói, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko …ìuri lo'ude non e cuu…ói …óin, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno …ìe annduno"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala huunde nde …ìe noddata gaanin Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  29,43,"∆äee ko mise …óe Men piyanta yim…ìe …ìen; ko woni tun, faamataa …óen, si wanaa anndu…ìe …ìen"
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii …óum, maande, wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  29,45,"Janngu kon ko waayinaa e maa…óa ka Deftere, √±ii…ìaa e julde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no ha…óa pankare e ko a√±inii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol …ìuri (huunde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko golloton kon"
  29,46,"Wata on wennjir yim…ìe Defte …ìen si wanaa e no …ìuri e mo∆¥∆¥irde, si wanaa hara ko …ìen too√±u…ìe e ma…ì…ìe. Wi'on: \"Men gom…óinii nden jippinaande e amen e …óen jippinaa…óe e mon. Rewetee…óo amen On e rewetee…óo mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Men jebbilanii …ìe Mo"
  29,47,"Ko wano non Men jippiniri e maa…óa Deftere nden. ∆Åen …ìe Men okki Deftere nden, hi…ìe gom…óini nde. Hino e ma…ì…ìe on gom…óin…óo nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa heefer…ìe …ìen"
  29,48,"A wonaano hi…óa janngaynoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano √±aamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnoo…ìe …ìen sikkittono"
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe e …ìer…óe …ìen okkaa…ìe ganndal. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa too√±u…ìe …ìen"
  29,50,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Hanno jippinee e makko maandeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jertinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  29,51,"Kere yonaali …ìe wonnde Men jippinii e maa…óa Deftere nden hinde janngee e ma…ì…ìe? Wonii e …óum, yurmeende e waaju wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe"
  29,52,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii hakkunde am e moo…óon seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. ∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe meere nden …ìe yeddi Alla, ko …ìen woni sooyu…ìe …ìen"
  29,53,"Hi…ìe hawjirane lepte …óen. Si wanaano fii lajal innaangal, lepte …óen ardirayno e ma…ì…ìe juhal, hara kam…ìe …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  29,54,"Hi…ìe hawjirane lepte …óen, hara non pellet, Jahannama ko fiiltiinge heefere…ìe …ìen"
  29,55,"√ëalnde lepte …óen suddiroyta …ìe senngo dow ma…ì…ìe e ka ley koy…óe ma…ì…ìe, O daala[na …ìe]: \"Mee…óee ko gollayno…óon kon"
  29,56,Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe! Anndee leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Ko Min woni ko rewoton
  29,57,Kala wonkii mee…óay maayde. Refti ko ka Amen ruttete…óon
  29,58,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, ma Men ho…ónu …ìe ka Aljanna e cuu…ói …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley majji, ko…ìe duumotoo…ìe ton. Iskin(heskey)¬∞ mo∆¥∆¥ere njo…ìdi gollunoo…ìe, @Corrected"
  29,59,"…ìen mu√±√±ii…ìe, …ìe tuugii e Joomi ma…ì…ìe"
  29,60,"∆äuu…óii e ruugay…ói …ói yoo…ìotaako arsike majji! Ko Alla arsikata …ói wonndude e onon. Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Anndu…óo"
  29,61,"Pellet, si a lanndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuu- li …óin e leydi ndin, O elti naange ngen e lewru ndu?\" Ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Ko honno …ìe ferlitoraa (e gom…óingol ngol)"
  29,62,"Alla no yaajinana arsike on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Himo …ìittana mo. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  29,63,"Pellet, si a lanndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu …óam O wuurnitiri leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorude?\", ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Alla\". Maaku: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla!\". Si ko woni, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe haqqiltaa"
  29,64,"∆äam nguurndam aduna wonaali, si wanaa mbelee…óe e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko ho…óo laakara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno …ìe annduno"
  29,65,"Si …ìe wa…ó…óike ka laana, …ìe nodda Alla …ìe la…ì…ìinano Mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde O da…óndi …ìe ka njorndi, ontuma …ìe sirka"
  29,66,"No …ìe yeddira ko Men okki …ìe kon, awa yo …ìe dakmito! Aray ka…ìe annda"
  29,67,"E …ìee yi'aali wonnde Men wa…óii hormorde hoolniinde, yim…ìe …ìen no cifee(bifte) bannge ma…ì…ìe? E ko meere nden …ìe gom…óinta …ìe yedda neemaaji Alla …óin"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo …ìuri too√±irde wa on fefindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  29,69,"∆Åen tii…ónor…ìe e (weltingol) Men, ma Men fewnir…ìe e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no wonndi e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"